            Kristen Ross is a Licensed Professional Counselor with over 14 years of experience in holistic health counseling. She integrates evidence-based approaches like CBT with mindfulness and somatic techniques to help clients find lasting relief from anxiety. Her whole-person approach addresses the mental, physical, and emotional dimensions of healing.
          </p>
